name: NetService.ErrorCode
desc: These constants identify errors that can occur when accessing net services.

items.name: case collisionError
items.desc: The service could not be published because the name is already in use. The name could be in use locally or on another system.

items.name: case notFoundError
items.desc: The service could not be found on the network.

items.name: case activityInProgress
items.desc: The net service cannot process the request at this time. No additional information about the network state is known.

items.name: case badArgumentError
items.desc: An invalid argument was used when creating the NSNetService object.

items.name: case invalidError
items.desc: The net service was improperly configured.

items.name: case timeoutError
items.desc: The net service has timed out.
